37
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:41,600
Don't worry about me.

38
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:42,560
Go.

39
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:43,600
The further, the better.

40
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:44,720
Go.

41
00:04:45,279 --> 00:04:46,160
Go.

42
00:04:46,879 --> 00:04:47,680
Don't worry about me.

43
00:04:47,680 --> 00:04:48,519
Go.

44
00:04:53,120 --> 00:04:54,000
Chi Hui,

45
00:04:54,879 --> 00:04:55,920
