46
00:04:56,759 --> 00:04:58,319
Let's meet in the next life.

47
00:06:10,560 --> 00:06:11,439
Where are you?

48
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:12,839
Rongzhou.

49
00:06:12,839 --> 00:06:13,439
Museum.

50
00:06:13,920 --> 00:06:14,519
Have you ever seen Jiang Xun and Shen Shutu

51
00:06:14,519 --> 00:06:16,519
