52
00:06:34,800 --> 00:06:36,240
I want to take this with me.

53
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:39,000
k

54
00:06:41,839 --> 00:06:42,839
Okay.

55
00:07:02,439 --> 00:07:04,000
Why do you ask?

56
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:05,439
It's none of your business.

57
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:07,399
Check if the sketchbook

58
00:07:07,399 --> 00:07:08,920
is in the studio.

59
00:08:11,759 --> 00:08:12,560
What's up?

60
00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:14,560
Shutu,

61
00:08:15,279 --> 00:08:17,639
I wish we could always be like this.

62
00:08:18,759 --> 00:08:20,120
Of course we can.

63
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:25,160
Shutu, let's go to Sweden together.

64
00:08:28,519 --> 00:08:29,879
Why do you say that?

65
00:08:30,399 --> 00:08:31,079
I...

66
00:08:32,279 --> 00:08:33,720
I'm just a little tired.

67
00:08:38,840 --> 00:08:39,639
It doesn't matter.

68
00:08:42,240 --> 00:08:44,519
If you're tired, just take a good rest.

69
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:47,120
Then we'll consider what to do next.

70
00:08:47,360 --> 00:08:48,279
Okay?

71
00:08:48,879 --> 00:08:49,679
Okay.

72
00:09:03,120 --> 00:09:04,240
How's it going?

73
00:09:06,039 --> 00:09:07,200
Shen Shutu said

74
00:09:07,679 --> 00:09:09,360
