75
00:09:09,600 --> 00:09:11,679
But I'm not sure if it's his conspiracy.

76
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:14,320
You only have 12 hours to hesitate.

77
00:09:14,759 --> 00:09:16,919
If you can't help us get Jiaotu No.1,

78
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:19,039
you will lose your value.

79
00:09:20,080 --> 00:09:21,519
You can't run away.

80
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:24,320
No matter where you go,

81
00:09:24,759 --> 00:09:26,559
we can find you.

82
00:10:00,039 --> 00:10:01,360
There are national security people in the museum.

83
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:03,279
Shen Shutu's amnesia is fake.

84
00:10:04,039 --> 00:10:05,080
If you don't fear death,

85
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:06,759
