86
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:08,360
Go get it yourself.

87
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:10,320
[Ke Yu'ang,]

88
00:10:10,720 --> 00:10:12,840
[we're in the same boat.]

89
00:10:13,120 --> 00:10:14,240
[If you keep dragging your feet,]

90
00:10:14,240 --> 00:10:15,360
[we'll both die.]

91
00:10:16,279 --> 00:10:17,360
[What do you want me to do?]

92
00:10:18,159 --> 00:10:20,159
[Abduct Jiang Xun when they're unprepared.]

93
00:10:20,519 --> 00:10:21,679
[I'll be]

94
00:10:21,679 --> 00:10:23,080
[at the dock to meet you.]

95
00:10:23,639 --> 00:10:24,879
[You want to turn the tables?]

96
00:10:27,039 --> 00:10:27,799
[Fine,]

97
00:10:28,039 --> 00:10:29,120
[but I have a condition.]

98
00:10:29,440 --> 00:10:30,519
Don't hurt Jiang Xun.

99
00:10:30,879 --> 00:10:31,759
After the job's done,

100
00:10:32,159 --> 00:10:33,240
I'll take her away.

101
00:10:40,679 --> 00:10:41,559
Dinner's ready.

102
00:10:42,159 --> 00:10:42,879
Come on.

103
00:10:43,039 --> 00:10:44,200
I made you something tasty.

104
00:10:50,720 --> 00:10:51,679
Shutu,

105
00:10:53,279 --> 00:10:54,159
I've made up my mind.

106
00:10:54,879 --> 00:10:56,440
I'm going back to Rongzhou with you

107
00:10:56,919 --> 00:10:57,720
to get engaged.

108
00:10:57,879 --> 00:10:58,519
Right now.

109
00:11:02,679 --> 00:11:03,840
Are you sure

110
00:11:04,360 --> 00:11:05,879
I'm the one you want to marry?

111
00:11:06,679 --> 00:11:07,480
I'm sure.

112
00:11:08,240 --> 00:11:09,159
I feel

113
00:11:09,600 --> 00:11:11,519
we are destined to be together.

114
00:11:21,320 --> 00:11:22,039
[Ke Yu'ang,]

115
00:11:22,480 --> 00:11:24,200
[I will arrive in Rongzhou this afternoon.]

116
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:26,480
[Find out where the comic book is placed.]

117
00:11:26,919 --> 00:11:28,240
Jiang Xun is avoiding me.

118
00:11:28,840 --> 00:11:30,080
The comic book is in the office.

119
00:11:30,159 --> 00:11:31,039
Go get it yourself.

120
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:35,759
Ke Yu'ang,

121
00:11:36,440 --> 00:11:37,879
you know who you are.

122
00:11:38,759 --> 00:11:40,639
We hope you can redeem yourself.

123
00:12:12,279 --> 00:12:13,039
[In the drama,]

124
00:12:13,039 --> 00:12:13,639
[Ke Yu'ang]

125
00:12:13,639 --> 00:12:16,440
[is an agent of a foreign espionage and intelligence agency.]

126
00:12:16,799 --> 00:12:18,840
[He participated in espionage activities,]

127
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:20,440
[which is a serious criminal offense.]

128
00:12:20,840 --> 00:12:22,279
[He should be severely punished according to the law.]

129
00:12:23,080 --> 00:12:24,840
[But under Jiang Xun's guidance,]

130
00:12:24,960 --> 00:12:25,720
he realized

131
00:12:25,720 --> 00:12:28,679
the shameless nature of the foreign espionage and intelligence agency.

132
00:12:28,679 --> 00:12:29,799
He suddenly woke up

133
00:12:29,879 --> 00:12:31,080
and stopped just in time.

134
00:12:31,279 --> 00:12:33,279
He assisted in foiling the enemy's plot.

135
00:12:33,679 --> 00:12:36,440
In the end, he redeemed himself.

136
00:12:36,879 --> 00:12:38,440
According to Article 68

137
00:12:38,440 --> 00:12:40,159
of the Criminal Law of the People's Republic of China,

138
00:12:40,240 --> 00:12:42,960
if a criminal makes significant contributions after committing a crime,

139
00:12:42,960 --> 00:12:45,120
the punishment can be reduced or exempted.
